those 10,000 photos.

00:19:44.330 --> 00:19:47.520
So what we really want to pull
out is a handful of photos

00:19:47.520 --> 00:19:51.720
that really represent, that
bring out the essence of what

00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:52.970
the Notre Dame looks like.

00:19:57.540 --> 00:20:03.740
One thing we want to capture is,
