would look like.

00:24:06.070 --> 00:24:09.060
So if you only took this
information and started to

00:24:09.060 --> 00:24:14.490
create a 3D slide show out of
this, you would end up with a

00:24:14.490 --> 00:24:16.610
lot of artifacts.

00:24:16.610 --> 00:24:19.750
Going from the photo on the far
