00:25:24.840 --> 00:25:28.276
material as you're going from
one photo that you're going to

00:25:28.276 --> 00:25:31.080
linger the camera on
to the next photo.

00:25:31.080 --> 00:25:33.790
So you have a lot of flexibility
in being able to

00:25:33.790 --> 00:25:36.110
identify photos that really give
you a very nice, smooth

00:25:36.110 --> 00:25:37.680
transition.

00:25:37.680 --> 00:25:40.850
You put all of this together,
and that ends up giving you a

00:25:40.850 --> 00:25:44.210
3D tour of the Notre Dame.

00:25:44.210 --> 00:25:47.580
We can do this not just for the
